  "title": "Mechanical Designer",
  "description": "<p>🚀 Mechanical Designer </p><p></p><p>Manufacturing Industry | Metal Cutting Machinery & Machine Tool Company</p><p>📍 Work Location: Pasir Ris (Blue Line EW1)</p><p>🕒 Full-Time | Monday – Friday</p><p>🎤 Interview: In-person / Offline</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>🌟 About the Company</p><p></p><p>We are a company in the manufacturing industry, specializing in the manufacturing and maintenance of metal cutting machinery and machine tools such as lathes, milling machines, and planers. Our secondary business includes the manufacturing of steel structures.</p><p></p><p>We are expanding and looking for a skilled Mechanical Designer to join our engineering team.</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>🔧 Job Responsibilities</p><p></p><p>You will be responsible for:</p><p>•\tDesigning and developing mechanical systems and machine tool structures</p><p>•\tHandling component design, improvement, and prototype development</p><p>•\tPreparing engineering drawings and technical documentation</p><p>•\tSupporting production by ensuring designs are practical and manufacturable</p><p>•\tWorking closely with production and maintenance teams for design optimization</p><p>•\tEnsuring design compliance with quality and safety standards</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>✅ Requirements</p><p></p><p>To qualify, candidates should have:</p><p>•\tMinimum 3 years of experience in:</p><p>•\tMechanical system design</p><p>•\tComponent development</p><p>•\tProduct prototype design</p><p>•\tKnowledge of manufacturing processes, especially:</p><p>•\tCNC machining / processing techniques</p><p>•\tProficiency in design tools such as:</p><p>•\tCAD (AutoCAD / SolidWorks / equivalent)</p><p>•\tExperience in machinery and machine tool design is highly preferred</p><p>•\tAble to work independently and as part of a team</p><p></p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>💰 Salary</p><p></p><p>$3,000 – $4,000/month (commensurate with experience)</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>🕘 Working Hours</p><p>•\tMonday – Friday: 8:15am – 6:00pm</p><p>•\t5-day work week</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>🏖 Leave Entitlement</p><p>•\tAnnual Leave: 8 days</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>📩 Apply Now</p><p></p><p>If you have strong mechanical design experience and would like to work in a stable manufacturing environment involving machine tools and industrial equipment, we welcome you to apply today!</p>",
